 memory. Others are simply reabsorbed into the "idian landscape. Remembering leaves its marks on the skin of the city, and the goal of this book is to analyze and understand precisely how.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / Urban.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362560040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503625600423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503625600/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles